<%- include('partials/header'); -%>

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>home</title>
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-QWTKZyjpPEjISv5WaRU9OFeRpok6YctnYmDr5pNlyT2bRjXh0JMhjY6hW+ALEwIH" crossorigin="anonymous">
<style>
    body {
    font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    background-color: #f8f9fa;
  }

    .about-cont {
      position: relative;
      display: inline-block;
    }

    .about-text {
      position: absolute;
      top: 50%;
      left: 50%;
      transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
      z-index: 1;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .about-text p {
      font-size: 20px;
      /* text-align: justify; */
    }

    .about-cont img {
      display: block;
      width: 80vw;
      max-height: 70vh;
      margin-left: 8rem;
      margin-bottom: 6rem;
    }

    header {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
    }
    .carousel{
      position: relative;
    }

    .containerss {
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 100px;
    }

    .containerss h1 {
      font-family: Lucida Handwriting;
      font-size: 3rem;
      color: #333;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 4px;
      position: relative;
      display: inline-block;
      padding-bottom: 10px;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
      background-image: linear-gradient(120deg, #e192e6, #da1dcd);
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    }
    .carousel-item{
      position: absolute;
    }

    .carousel {
      margin-top: var(--header-height); 
    }

    .carousel-item img {
      height: calc(90vh - var(--header-height));
      object-fit: cover;
    }

    .carousel-item img{
      padding:-10px;
      height: 90vh;
    }


</style>
</head>
<body>
  <div id="carouselExample" class="carousel slide" style="margin-top:12vh;margin-bottom: 12vh;">
      <div class="carousel-inner">
        <div class="carousel-item active">
          <img src="h1.webp" class="d-block w-100" alt="...">
        </div>
        <div class="carousel-item">
          <img src="nikaah.jpg" class="d-block w-100" alt="...">
        </div>
        <div class="carousel-item">
          <img src="home3.jpg" class="d-block w-100" alt="...">
        </div>
      </div>
      <button class="carousel-control-prev" type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExample" data-bs-slide="prev">
        <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        <span class="visually-hidden">Previous</span>
      </button>
      <button class="carousel-control-next" type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExample" data-bs-slide="next">
        <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        <span class="visually-hidden">Next</span>
      </button>
    </div>

    <div class="containerss" style="margin-top:20vh;">
      <h1>About Us</h1>
    </div>

    <div class="about-cont">
      <div class="about-text">
        <p>Blissful Union is more than just a wedding planning service; it's a sanctuary where love blossoms and dreams come to life. With a dedicated team of wedding enthusiasts, we craft unforgettable moments that celebrate the beauty of love and commitment. Our mission is simple: to turn your wedding dreams into reality. From intimate ceremonies to grand celebrations, we provide personalized services that reflect your unique love story and vision. With meticulous attention to detail and unwavering professionalism, we ensure that every aspect of your special day is perfect. Let us be your trusted partner on this journey towards happily ever after.</p>
      </div>
      <img src="about.png" alt="About Us">
    </div>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-YvpcrYf0tY3lHB60NNkmXc5s9fDVZLESaAA55NDzOxhy9GkcIdslK1eN7N6jIeHz" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
      
</body>

